flowchart LR
A[Client: Donate Form] --> B[POST /api/payments/create]
B --> C{Country routing on backend}
C -->|IN| D[Razorpay: create order]
C -->|Non-IN| E[Stripe: create checkout session]
D --> F[Client opens Razorpay checkout]
E --> G[Client redirects to Stripe checkout]

F --> H[Razorpay Webhook]
G --> I[Stripe Webhook]

H --> J[Verify signature + persist event in Supabase]
I --> J
J --> K[Idempotent state transition: pending -> paid]
K --> L[Enqueue receipt_email job in Supabase]

L --> M[POST /api/jobs/receipt-email]
M --> N[Generate receipt PDF with PDFKit]
N --> O[Upload receipt to Supabase Storage]
O --> P[Download static NGO PDF from Supabase Storage]
P --> Q[Send email via Resend]
Q --> R[Mark receipt/email delivered]